{"title":"安宁","authors":["皮奥乌斯·奥列盖"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":3,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"安宁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔尼日利亚〕皮奥乌斯·奥列盖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，你眯上眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动也不动，这是安宁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当大雷雨击起闪电的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在牢房里也很安宁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可我们难道需要这样的安宁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，朋友！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比起退却，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在斗争中你会冒更大的风险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而你却能赢得胜利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺起胸膛迎接海的风暴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上保持住镇静。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔周尊南　译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}